{"tid":1175390,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"手提電腦唔知壞咩","createTime":"2019-05-28T13:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T13:48:53.000Z","uid":138311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1cd66932be9d737fe7cd15580ec081ba51b2d562","tid":1175390,"uid":138311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:38:51.000Z","msg":"小弟用緊Asus K570UD，咁本來都正正常常，不過依幾日開始有d問題：（已經洗完機但問題都冇改善）<br />\n<br />\n1.右鍵桌面一直轉圈圈同工作列冇反應（但開完工作管理員工作列又正常禁到）<br />\n<br />\n2.會成日lag住一個頁面（例如我開個skype就會突然lag住，禁咩制都冇反應）<br />\n<br />\n3. 用滑鼠冇反應，用鍵盤就有反應（例如我部電腦開機要打pin碼，用滑鼠點極頁面都冇反應，反而鍵盤禁就有反應）<br />\n<br />\n以上問題唔知點解只要禁ctrl+Alt+Del開工作管理員就可以唔lag一小時間，有冇巴打知道喺咩問題又可以簡單解決到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔得嘅話就打算去Asus維修中心整"},{"pid":"9118ae40219ba4573b8136e3cb86bf1ef06e8585","tid":1175390,"uid":113922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:40:14.000Z","msg":"重裝最新windows"},{"pid":"fc849ba7fce614bb5320b653d44e2c61a3d424cc","tid":1175390,"uid":40961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:41:41.000Z","msg":"hdd 100% usage?"},{"pid":"ff9c72b5b9bd29eab5585980caa2ada0bf3df3a6","tid":1175390,"uid":42760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:42:37.000Z","msg":"Check harddisk"},{"pid":"f122ea7bb07dd84dbd093e0ccf78ac0d6e044e84","tid":1175390,"uid":138311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc849ba7fce614bb5320b653d44e2c61a3d424cc","tid":1175390,"uid":40961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:41:41.000Z","msg":"hdd 100% usage?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:46:48.000Z","msg":"部機得sdd， 我睇返工作管理員冇100%使用率"},{"pid":"6f0599e266aeef536be5e1e489b0e510604b9f85","tid":1175390,"uid":138311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff9c72b5b9bd29eab5585980caa2ada0bf3df3a6","tid":1175390,"uid":42760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:42:37.000Z","msg":"Check harddisk"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:48:53.000Z","msg":"手提電腦可以點check，我硬件嘢唔熟，又唔敢亂拆部機（因為仲有2個月保養）所以先想問下各位巴打有冇試過類似情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}